From: Murray S. Kucherawy <msk@trusteddomain.org>
To: opendmarc-announce@trusteddomain.org, opendmarc-users@trusteddomain.org
Subject: OpenDMARC v0.1.0 released

The Trusted Domain Project is pleased to announce the availability of
OpenDMARC v0.1.0, now available for download from SourceForge.

This is a beta release.  It is still undergoing shakedown in various production
environments.  You are welcome to download it and try it in your environment.
*PLEASE* provide feedback about any bugs you find or suggestions you may
have via the opendmarc-users mailing list.

The full RELEASE_NOTES for this version:

1.0.0		2012/07/??
	Initial release.

0.1.0		2012/07/07
	Initial Beta release.

Please use the mailing lists at http://www.trusteddomain.org/ to report
problems, make suggestions, or as questions.  After the first formal
release (v1.0.0) we will begin using bug tracking software for specific
requests, but the lists will be used for general support and other dialog.

Welcome to OpenDMARC!

The Trusted Domain Project
